(10, '{\"bn\":null,\"en\":\"Is one week enough time for doing Umrah?\"}', '{\"bn\":null,\"en\":\"Umrah won\'t take over multi day, different days you can see others supplicating and witness the excellence of Makkah. Counting your 2 long stretches of movement you can perform Umrah in 7 days. Completing Umrah in 1 week is possible. There are 7 days Umrah packages available from which you can choose.\"}', '{\"bn\":null,\"en\":\"<h4>Is one week enough time for doing Umrah?<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Umrah won\'t take over multi day, different days you can see others supplicating and witness the excellence of Makkah. Counting your 2 long stretches of movement you can perform Umrah in 7 days. Completing Umrah in 1 week is possible. There are 7 days Umrah packages available from which you can choose.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Hajj can be performed just at a particular time in the year, yet for Umrah there is no detail to perform in a specific time. Muslims from over the globe travel to the Holy Cities of Makkah and Madinah. Be that as it may, there are unquestionably couple of things one needs to consider before you go for it. Moreover. pioneers have an inquiry that would they be able to performed entire Umrah in 1 week or they would have to go for multi week Umrah? Well, yes it is possible to complete Umrah in 1 week. All things considered, it is all that anyone could need to perform Umrah. The system isn\'t long.<\\/p>\"}', 'is-one-week-enough-time-for-doing-umrah', NULL, '1726309194.png', 1, 1, 'published', 1, 1438, 1, 3, '2024-01-17 09:55:48', '2026-03-30 03:18:44');
